%% CLI Command Execution Sequence
%% Typical command lifecycle

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant CLI
    participant Config
    participant Core
    participant FS as File System

    User->>CLI: Run command with args
    CLI->>CLI: Parse arguments
    CLI->>Config: Load config file
    Config-->>CLI: Settings
    CLI->>Core: Execute command
    Core->>FS: Read/write files
    FS-->>Core: Result
    Core-->>CLI: Output
    CLI-->>User: Display result
